OL,3,C28 recommendations to strengthen
OL,4,Csafeguarding in assisted dying
OL,5,Cproposals
OL,7,F"Detailed operational guidance is
OL,8,Frequired, particularly in relation to
OL,9,Fcoercion, decision-making capacity,
OL,10,Fthe waiver, practitioner experience,
OL,11,Ftraining, public awareness, and
OL,12,Ffinancial preparedness," the scrutiny
OL,13,Fpanel states in its report.
OL,15,F"The recommendations provide a clear
OL,16,Fpathway to strengthen the framework
OL,17,Fand seek to ensure that assisted
OL,18,Fdying, if introduced in Jersey, is
OL,19,Fdelivered safely, ethically, and with
OL,20,Fthe highest possible degree of public
OL,21,Fconfidence."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/16
