OL,7,FRecommendations 1-7: Palliative Care
OL,8,Fand End-of-Life Services
OL,10,FThe Panel says that the current
OL,11,Flegislation shows a clear duty to
OL,12,Fprovide end-of-life care before an
OL,13,Findividual can pursue an assisted
OL,14,Fdying service.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/16
