OL,5,Cproposals
OL,7,FThe Panel also wants data on the use
OL,8,Fof the pause mechanism and the
OL,9,Ftimeliness of palliative assessments
OL,10,Fto be published to ensure vulnerable
OL,11,Fgroups aren't being exposed to
OL,12,Fpotential risks.
OL,14,FProcess and Safeguards: Administering,
OL,15,FDecision-making, Coercion, Funding,
OL,16,FImplementation (8-18)
