OL,4,Csafeguarding in assisted dying
OL,5,Cproposals
OL,7,FTo protect vulnerable people from
OL,8,Fbeing coerced into an assisted death,
OL,9,Fkey recommendations also highly
OL,10,Fsuggest including safeguarding, mental
OL,11,Fcapacity, and social care specialists
OL,12,Fin coercion assessments to get
OL,13,Fmultiple professional perspectives on
OL,14,Fwhether someone is being coerced.
OL,16,FThey also strongly recommend approving
OL,17,Fan amendment to remove third-party
OL,18,Fappeals from people with a "special
OL,19,Finterest" in a person's care.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/16
