OL,5,Cproposals
OL,7,FThe Panel also says that a
OL,8,Fcomprehensive financial impact
OL,9,Fassessment should be published for the
OL,10,Fassisted dying service, with clear
OL,11,Fbudgetary breakdowns published
OL,12,Fregularly, as well as financial
OL,13,Freviews.
OL,15,FRecommendations 19-22: Training and
OL,16,FGuidance
OL,18,FThe Panel found that training is a
OL,19,F"core safeguard" which needs
OL,20,F"significant development" in the
OL,21,Fproposed legislation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/16
