OL,5,Cproposals
OL,7,FIt has lodged an amendment to embed
OL,8,Frigorous training so practitioners can
OL,9,Fdetect coercion, undue influence,
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse indicators, and
OL,11,Ffinancial coercion.
OL,13,FThe recommendations listed at least
OL,14,Feight modules to include in training,
OL,15,Fincluding ethical reasoning, mental
OL,16,Fcapacity assessments, and
OL,17,Fcommunicating with disabled and
OL,18,Fvulnerable individuals.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/16
