OL,7,FUpdates to those training materials
OL,8,Fare advised to use evidence from
OL,9,Findependent national and international
OL,10,Fsources, recommending that guidance
OL,11,Ffor professionals should be published
OL,12,Fat least six months before the
OL,13,Fproposals become law.
OL,15,FRecommendations 23-28: Public awareness
OL,17,FThe Panel hopes that raising public
OL,18,Fawareness will ensure that islanders
OL,19,Fcan make informed decisions, but noted
OL,20,Fthat real-world accessibility will be
OL,21,Fvital.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/16
