OL,5,Cproposals
OL,7,FTo ensure vulnerable residents, older
OL,8,Fadults, and those without digital
OL,9,Faccess are not excluded, the Panel
OL,10,Frecommends that an 'Accessibility
OL,11,FAnnex' be attached to any guidance,
OL,12,Fspecifying the use of audio, large
OL,13,Fprint, plain language, and physical
OL,14,Fcopies.
OL,16,FPublic materials should also include
OL,17,Fwhat to do if an islander feels
OL,18,Fpressured by a decision, and explain
OL,19,Fthe law's emphasis on voluntariness
OL,20,Fand capacity checks.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/16
